snippet.title: Amber Heard posts topless Insta pic from Bali vacation
snippet.description: American actress Amber Heard has landed in Bali and there are pics to prove iteven a topless one.  Dont get too excited though, the 31-year-old ex-wife of Johnny Depp kept it tasteful and just posed in her bikini bottoms at what appears to be a private rooftop pool, with her back to the camera, simply captioning the shot, When in Bali. A post shared by Amber Heard (@amberheard) on Sep 11, 2017 at 7:22am PDTApparently recovering from her recent breakup from billionaire boyfriend Elon Musk, Heard is accompanied in Bali by close friend Raquel Pennington and assistant, Savannah McMillan. Theres a video of Heard and Pennington donning matching white outfits, getting their groove on to some Balinese beats, with the two swinging their hips to the music.  Indonesian Instagrammers seem thrilled to see Heard in the archipelago nation, with a number of comments on her video reading Welcome to Bali!. Hello Bali!A post shared by Amber Heard (@amberheard) on Sep 10, 2017 at 8:03am PDTIn the same outfits, the two pose in a black and white shot, and another photo posted to Heards account shows them eating sashimi.
